snippet.title: Big Green Breakfast Smoothie | Amber Locke
snippet.description:
Amber’s back with another delicious raw vegan recipe – the Big Green Breakfast Smoothie. Jam packed with more fruit and veg than you’d be able to eat in one go, bursting with nutrients and topped with luscious goji berries this healthy smoothie is sure to set you off to a good start.

If you like Amber's recipe please give this video a thumbs up and leave a comment in the box below. 

Find the recipe here: http://www.jamieoliver.com/recipes/member-recipes/recipe-detail/4696/#z66uqPF5MkgVM7mx.97

What’s your favourite food to start the day?  Let us know in the comment box below - we'd love to hear from you.
